      "content": "oh i see. but i read a health blog saying grapefruit is actually super good for heart health and helps with inflammation. since i'm already taking the pill for my cholesterol, wouldnt the vitamins in the juice actually help the medicine work better? it seems like it should be fine in small amounts, right?",
