      "content": "really? i'm kinda a health nut so i hate missing out on vitamins. if i just have like a tiny splash of it in my smoothie instead of a whole glass, is that still going to be a big deal? i don't want to deal with all the side effects, but i really want those antioxidants. surely a little bit won't cause a toxic buildup?",
